name: Angela
bio: Love to party, love going on adventures. Also Netflix and Chill.

name: Pam
bio: I love roller coasters but the pirate ship ride completely terrifies me. I once backpacked around Lake Tahoe in 13 days. When I was 14 I got a concussion swing dancing.

name: Caro
bio: About Me: I like to sing-talk, guys with messy hair, reading the New Yorker on Sunday mornings, and funny voices. About You: If you’re still reading, that’s pretty good. Let’s do this.

name: Sara
bio: All happy girls are alike; every unhappy girl is unhappy in her own way. My kind of unhappy is full of self-deprecating humor, double IPAs, and is actually pretty rad. Let me know if you want to be miserable together.

name: Marie
bio: I live my whole life setting up situations that will eventually lead to the phrase, “And then laughter and hilarity ensued…” Hoping this one will work out too.
